a><a class=\"font-medium transition-colors border-b-2 pb-[2px] text-on-surface-variant border-transparent hover:text-primary\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/events\">Events</a><a class=\"font-medium transition-colors border-b-2 pb-[2px] text-on-surface-variant border-transparent hover:text-primary\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/resources\">Resources</a><div class=\"relative group\"><button class=\"flex items-center gap-1 font-medium text-on-surface-variant transition-colors group-hover:text-primary bg-transparent border-none cursor-pointer\">Office<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-lg leading-none transform group-hover:rotate-180 transition-transform\">expand_more</span></button><div class=\"absolute top-full -left-10 w-56 opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-300 z-50 py-3 mt-4 bg-surface/95 backdrop-blur-md border border-outline-variant/30 rounded-xl shadow-xl\"><a class=\"block px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/news\">District News</a><a class=\"block px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/newsletter\">Newsletters</a><a class=\"block px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/jobs\">Jobs</a><a class=\"block px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/brand-centre\">Brand Hub</a><a class=\"block px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/hall-of-fame\">Hall of Fame</a><a class=\"block px-6 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/leaderboard\">Leaderboard</a></div></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6\"><a class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-3xl cursor-pointer transition-all hover:scale-110 text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" href=\"/admin\">account_circle</a><button class=\"md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle Menu\" style=\"color:var(--color-primary);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-3xl\">menu</span></button></div></div></nav><main class=\"flex-grow flex flex-col\"><main><section class=\"relative py-32 px-6 overflow-hidden\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle)\"><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[.3em] mb-8 inline-block\" style=\"background:rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.1);border:1px solid rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.3);color:var(--color-reef)\">The District Authority</span><h1 class=\"text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-none\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest)\">Architecting <br/><span class=\"gradient-text\">Social Change.</span></h1><p class=\"text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--text-secondary)\">Rotaract District 3192 is a thriving network of young leaders committed to institutional excellence and sustainable community impact.</p></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-24\"><div class=\"card group p-8 \"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 mb-6 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\" style=\"background:rgba(14, 107, 168, 0.2)\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-3xl\" style=\"color:var(--color-reef)\">rocket_launch</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest);font-family:&#x27;Space Grotesk&#x27;, sans-serif\">Our Mission</h3><p class=\"leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--text-secondary)\">To provide opportunities for young men and women to enhance their knowledge and skills that will assist them in personal development, to address the physical and social needs of their communities, and to promote better relations between all people worldwide through a framework of friendship and service.</p></div><div class=\"card group p-8 \"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 mb-6 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center transition-transform group-hover:scale-110\" style=\"background:rgba(240, 165, 0, 0.15)\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-3xl\" style=\"color:var(--color-gold)\">visibility</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest);font-family:&#x27;Space Grotesk&#x27;, sans-serif\">Our Vision</h3><p class=\"leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--text-secondary)\">Together, we see a world where young people unite and take action to create lasting change — across the globe, in our communities, and in ourselves. We aim to be the premier leadership development organization for young professionals in South India.</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden aspect-video relative group\" style=\"border:1px solid var(--border-subtle)\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559027615-cd4451d13488?auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;q=80&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Service\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-end p-12\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(to top, rgba(2,11,24,0.9), rgba(2,11,24,0.2))\"><div class=\"max-w-xl\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-4\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest)\">Service Above Self</h3><p class=\"font-medium leading-relaxed\" style=\"color:var(--text-secondary)\">Through every project and every handshake, we aim to build a legacy of excellence that transcends generations.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block\" style=\"color:var(--color-reef)\">District Core Team</span><h2 class=\"text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest)\">Strategic Leadership</h2></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"card group p-6 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-6\" style=\"border:1px solid var(--border-subtle)\"><img src=\"https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Priya+Ramesh&amp;background=0e6ba8&amp;color=caf0f8&amp;size=400\" alt=\"Dr. Priya Ramesh\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-1\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest)\">Dr. Priya Ramesh</h3><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\" style=\"color:var(--color-reef)\">District Rotaract Representative</p></div><div class=\"card group p-6 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-6\" style=\"border:1px solid var(--border-subtle)\"><img src=\"https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Rahul+Krishnan&amp;background=00b4d8&amp;color=020b18&amp;size=400\" alt=\"Rahul Krishnan\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-1\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest)\">Rahul Krishnan</h3><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\" style=\"color:var(--color-reef)\">District Secretary</p></div><div class=\"card group p-6 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-6\" style=\"border:1px solid var(--border-subtle)\"><img src=\"https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Sneha+Venkatesh&amp;background=0e6ba8&amp;color=caf0f8&amp;size=400\" alt=\"Sneha Venkatesh\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-1\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest)\">Sneha Venkatesh</h3><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\" style=\"color:var(--color-reef)\">District Treasurer</p></div><div class=\"card group p-6 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300\"><div class=\"aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-6\" style=\"border:1px solid var(--border-subtle)\"><img src=\"https://ui-avatars.com/api/?name=Karthik+Reddy&amp;background=00b4d8&amp;color=020b18&amp;size=400\" alt=\"Karthik Reddy\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-1\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest)\">Karthik Reddy</h3><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\" style=\"color:var(--color-reef)\">Professional Service Chair</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-12\" style=\"color:var(--color-crest)\">The Legacy of 3192</h2><div class=\"space-y-6 text-lg font-medium leading-relaxed text-left\" style=\"color:var(--text-secondary)\"><p>Rotaract originally began as a Rotary International youth program in 1968 at Charlotte North Rotary Club in Charlotte, North Carolina, USA. Today, Rotaract operates globally with over 10,000 clubs in 180 countries.</p><p>District 3192 has a rich legacy of vibrant youth action in South India. Formed to concentrate impact within key urban and rural demographics, 3192 acts as a catalyst for professional development and massive community service projects.</p><p>Our authority is derived from our commitment to institutional excellence and the tangible impact we create in the lives of those we serve.</p></div><div class=\"mt-20 p-12 rounded-[2rem]\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(5,30,56,0.9) 0%, rgba(10,53,96,0.7) 100%);border:1px solid rgba(14, 107, 168, 0.4)\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-6 italic\" style=\"color:var(--color-reef)\">&quot;Friendship through Service&quot;</h3><p class=\"font-medium mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto\" style=\"color:var(--text-secondary)\">Join a global movement of young leaders making an impact. Start your journey with Rotaract District 3192 today.</p><a href=\"/clubs\" class=\"btn-primary\" style=\"display:inline-flex\">Find a local club</a></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer style=\"background:rgba(2, 11, 24, 0.95);border-top:1px solid rgba(14, 107, 168, 0.25);backdrop-filter:blur(20px)\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 py-4 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-4\"><span class=\"text-sm font-bold tracking-tight whitespace-nowrap\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg, #00b4d8, #caf0f8);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text\">Rotaract · District 3192</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 flex-wrap\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-medium transition-colors\" style=\"color:var(--text-muted)\" href=\"/privacy\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\" style=\"font-size:14px\">shield</span>Privacy</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-medium transition-colors\" style=\"color:var(--text-muted)\" href=\"/terms\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\" style=\"font-size:14px\">gavel</span>Terms</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-xs font-medium transition-colors\" style=\"color:var(--text-muted)\" href=\"/cookies\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\" style=\"font-size:14px\">cookie</span>Cookies</a></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><a href=\"https://linkedin.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"LinkedIn\" class=\"transition-all hover:scale-110 hover:-translate-y-0.5\" style=\"color:var(--text-